text: The Trump Administration has refused to send a bipartisan congressional delegation to the UN this year — blocking my official participation but not my Republican counterpart’s. This isn’t the strong showing of unity and cooperation that we need at the UN.
To everyone celebrating Rosh Hashanah — Shana Tova! As I spend time with my family, I’m wishing you all peace, joy, and sweetness as we start the new year.
